tests.name: autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger keyboard interaction down arrow If the textbox is not empty and the listbox is displayed, moves visual focus to the first suggested value.
tests.suite: Autocomplete.test.tsx > autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger > keyboard interaction > down arrow

tests.name: autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger keyboard interaction down arrow If the textbox is empty and the listbox is not displayed, opens the listbox and moves visual focus to the first option.
tests.suite: Autocomplete.test.tsx > autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger > keyboard interaction > down arrow

tests.name: autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger keyboard interaction alt + down arrow Opens the listbox without moving focus or changing selection.
tests.suite: Autocomplete.test.tsx > autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger > keyboard interaction > alt + down arrow

tests.name: autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger keyboard interaction up arrow If the textbox is not empty and the listbox is displayed, moves visual focus to the last suggested value.
tests.suite: Autocomplete.test.tsx > autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger > keyboard interaction > up arrow

tests.name: autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger keyboard interaction up arrow If the textbox is empty, first opens the listbox if it is not already displayed and then moves visual focus to the last option.
tests.suite: Autocomplete.test.tsx > autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger > keyboard interaction > up arrow

tests.name: autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger keyboard interaction enter Closes the listbox if it is displayed.
tests.suite: Autocomplete.test.tsx > autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger > keyboard interaction > enter

tests.name: autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger keyboard interaction escape If the listbox is displayed, closes it.
tests.suite: Autocomplete.test.tsx > autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger > keyboard interaction > escape

tests.name: autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger keyboard interaction escape If the listbox is not displayed, clears the textbox.
tests.suite: Autocomplete.test.tsx > autocomplete[aria-autocomplete="list"] textbox trigger > keyboard interaction > escape
